'''Ahilyum''' ( s tinglizt : Helium) iga t [[Afrḍis akimyan|ufrḍis akimi]] lli mu gan tasdugmt n '''He''' d  uṭṭun afrḍas 2. Ur dar-s [[Aklu|akʷlu]], aḍu d tamimt, ur iga toxic, iga ulmig ''(inert)'', ar ittga agaz n yan ufrḍis ''(monoatomic gaz)'', d iga amzwaru ɣ trabut n igazen usmiden ''(the noble gas)'' ɣ [[taflwit tazdawant n ifrḍisn]].

'''Ahilyum''' iga wissin ifrḍisn ɣ tfessi d tugt ɣ umaḍal ([[Ahidrujin]] ad igan amzwaru ɣ tfessi d tugt), iga 24% n [[Tamtta|tmtta]], d uncek mqqurn gis ittuskar s ''nuclear fusion'' n [[Ahidrujin|uhidrujin]] ɣ [[itran]].<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helium</ref>

